-----------------------------------------------------------------
 Introduction
-----------------------------------------------------------------

HiPi provides interfaces to the Raspberry Pi GPIO together with
wrappers for some common libraries and peripherals.

It provides a Wx GUI application for managing some kernel device
drivers and setting the GPIO pin properties.

----------------------------------------------------------------
 Installation
----------------------------------------------------------------

see the INSTALL file.

